data.description: McDonald Hills Subdvision has always been a much sought after location. Located across the street from McDonld Hill Golf Course, this 3 bedroom, 1 bath home is a real deal. Holston River, one of East Tennessee's best fishing spots,  is only minutes away and so is Cherokee Lake. Historic downtown Rogersville is coming a go to restaurant destination and is only minutes away. Located outside the city limits, so no city taxes or restrictions. FIBER OPTIC INTERNET  Updates made in 2017 include new kitchen, new bath, heat pump, windows and doors. Hardwood floors, ceramic tile and lots of natural light in this brick ranch home. Level yard with a fenced back yard for animals or children to play.  Call today for an appointment to view this bargain. Information deemed reliable but not guaranteed. Buyer/buyer's agent to verify all information.
